1. Nationality:argentine == Color:ivory
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:ferret
3. Nationality:polish == Beverage:iced-tea
4. Color:amber is on the left of Color:grey
5. Color:amber == Beverage:sprite
6. Cigar:siglo == Pet:rabbit
7. Color:chestnut == Cigar:cain
8. Beverage:hot-chocolate is in the middle
9. Nationality:indian is on the far left
10. Cigar:swisher is on the left or right of Pet:guinea-pig
11. Pet:snakes is on the left or right of Cigar:cain
12. Cigar:light-vegafina == Beverage:cola
13. Nationality:turkish == Cigar:oliveros
14. Nationality:indian is on the left or right of Color:light-blue
15. Cigar:swisher is on the left or right of Beverage:mirinda

